(firstQuint)Implemental Flutter Mucus Clearance Devices on Geriatric Lung Function.

 Respiratory diseases are still increasing in the elderly population.

 The fluttering mucus clearance technique is expected to be a physical assisting therapy enhancing airway secretion clearance but needs more clinical randomized, controlled trial evidence.

